import Page from "../common/Page"; import classes from "./ProfilePage.module.css"; import {useState, useEffect, useContext} from "react" import {getCurrentUser} from '../../../api/UserApi' import AuthContext from '../../../store/auth-context'; const ProfilePage = () => { const [user, setUser] = useState({}) const [edit, setEdit] = useState(false) const authCtx = useContext(AuthContext) const toggleEdit = () => { setEdit(prevState => !prevState) } useEffect(() => { if(authCtx.isLoggedIn){ getCurrentUser(authCtx.token) .then((data) => { setUser(data); }) .catch((err) => { alert(err.message); }); } }, [authCtx]) return (
